Once upon a time, in a mysterious town surrounded by dense fog, Scooby-Doo and Mickey Mouse found themselves on an unexpected adventure. They had received a cryptic message on a torn piece of paper that led them to this eerie place. Unsure of what awaited them, the two iconic characters stood at a crossroad in the town square.

To the left, there was a narrow, dimly lit alley with graffiti-covered walls. To the right, a cobblestone path led toward an old, spooky mansion bathed in moonlight. 

Which path should Scooby-Doo and Mickey Mouse choose? 
Type 'left' or 'right' to continue the story.